### Example 01 — replicate from remote OData V4 into local DB
### Health checks against the provider and the consumer.

### LogisticsService (bundled CAP provider) — direct ping
GET http://localhost:4455/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$top=2

### Example consumer — is the service alive? (target table may still be empty)
GET http://localhost:4101/odata/v4/example/Shipments?$top=2

### Management service — is the pipeline registered?
GET http://localhost:4101/pipeline/Pipelines?$filter=name eq 'Shipments'
